WEBVTT

00:06:01.640 --> 00:06:06.176
I did research and volunteered
to help with fund-raising events,

00:06:06.200 --> 00:06:07.976
and whenever I could,

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:12.496
I talked with those who had
survived their own suicidal crisis

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:13.720
or attempt.

00:06:14.840 --> 00:06:17.056
One of the most helpful
conversations I had

00:06:17.080 --> 00:06:18.536
was with a coworker

00:06:18.560 --> 00:06:20.465
who overheard me talking to someone else

00:06:20.489 --> 00:06:21.689
in my office cubicle.

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:26.176
She heard me say
that Dylan could not have loved me

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:28.960
if he could do something
as horrible as he did.

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:31.800
Later, when she found me alone,